title: Swatch Irony Speed Up Black Dial Stainless Steel Men's Watch YVS441G
description: The Speed Up by Swatch is a timeless piece for those who value the little luxuries in life This watch is handcrafted with a sleek stainless-steel band and stainless steel case These durable materials guarantee longevity of the product and a proud owner in the years to come The multicolor band black dial and silver hands contribute to the overall appearance of the watch by adding a sophisticated aspect This piece also features a sturdy mineral crystal to protect the dial and a swiss quartz movement to ensure you remain punctual in your daily life In addition this product is water-resistant to 30 meters 100 feet 3 atm which is ideal for those days where an accident may occur The rich details imperishable components and luxurious quality of the Swatch Speed Up watch make it a perfect addition to any collection
